wlanpi-usb-ethernet (1.5.0) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Add sleep/wake cycle detection using USB suspend flags
  * Implement post-wake fast reset for iPad/iPhone recovery with configurable threshold
  * Add HOST_IS_SLEEPING state to prevent resets during host sleep
  * Refactor into modular functions with proper state management
  * Add diagnostic logging system with DEBUG_MODE support
  * Add optional boot timing logs for debugging enumeration issues
  * Implement ARP-based host discovery with caching
  * Support both usb0 (CDC ECM) and usb1 (RNDIS) interfaces simultaneously
  * Add dynamic sleep intervals based on connection state
  * Implement failure counting with configurable thresholds
  * Add dwc2 blacklist modprobe config for proper enumeration
  * Improve systemd service with better dependencies and restart logic
  * Refactor postinst for idempotent config.txt handling
  * Fix race conditions in USB gadget initialization
  * Improve error handling and logging

 -- Josh Schmelzle <josh@joshschmelzle.com>  Sat, 31 Jan 2026 00:00:00 -0500

